Date: 2002-05-25

Title: Towards chaos criterion in quantum field theory

Authors: V.I. Kuvshinov, A.V. Kuzmin

Comments: 7 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. A296 (2002) 82-86

Chaos criterion for quantum field theory is proposed. Its correspondence withclassical chaos criterion in semi-classical regime is shown. It is demonstratedfor real scalar field that proposed chaos criterion can be used to investigatestability of classical solutions of field equations.